Which moon has birthed you

Oh beautiful myna we waited for this day, you entered the in laws door
Tamhich koori cholum armane che wuchut paes ne chem yiwaan
Oh my daughter i have lived the dream i can't express
Hawale e karmakh peeri peeranas sui rachi chenis shuir paanas
My beloved i hand you to divine master who shall take care of your child like innocence daughter
